te bound states in\na kinetic model, a unified picture emerges in which symporter, antiporter, and\nuniporter function are extremes in a continuum of functionality. We briefly\ndiscuss how biological complexity may be integrated in quantitative kinetic\nmodels to provide a bridge from structure to function.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 00:52:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2021 04:46:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Dec 2021 19:14:37 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 23 Feb 2022 22:28:57 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2022 23:12:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-25"}
