f no symmetries exist. Finally, two explicit examples\nwill be given -- the classic Vlasov-Maxwell and the drift-kinetic\nVlasov-Maxwell -- and the results expressed in the language of regular vector\ncalculus for familiarity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 13:41:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 07:51:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-30"}
