 approach to large $N$ in the $Sp(2N)$ theories considered. We\nbriefly discuss their high-temperature behaviour, where symmetry restoration\nand enhancement are expected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 14:09:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 16:25:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-06"}
